1.0.name: wordpress/incarnate-for-wordpress
1.0.description: Incarnate for WordPress brings a rich avatar experience to your comments. Enter a handle from the web and easily select an avatar for a comment from providers like Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, MySpace and Gravatar.
